  "texts": [
    "An IRS was leveraged by Wang et al. [175] to cancel the multi-user interference (MUI) in the ISAC system.",
    "Specifically, the MUI energy was minimized subject to the CRB constraint via joint waveform and passive beamforming design.",
    "Bazzi and Chafii in [176] minimized the MUI energy under the PAPR and waveform similarity constraints.• Trade-off design.",
    "Different from the above-mentioned two counterparts, the trade-off design maximizes/minimizes the weighted sum of communication and sensing metrics to achieve the performance trade-off between the two functionalities.",
    "Moreover, this approach can keep a flexible balance between the two functionalities via changing the weighting coefficient."
  ],
